text: Tallangatta is a closed station located in the town of Tallangatta, on the Cudgewa railway line in Victoria, Australia. Today there is nothing left of the station. The turntable at Tallangatta was abolished in 1976. ==References== Category:Disused railway stations in Victoria (Australia) Category:Railway stations in Australia opened in 1891 Category:Railway stations closed in 1981 Category:1981 disestablishments in Australia
